:"j落都唔係好老姐"},{"pid":"3d9b83384b4cc93ab989176a195384306b441e64","tid":851471,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a7ef43dc84f18da153e99eb347decfcea495e2","tid":851471,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8149caffcacec9e213c25d1e175377aafafd1a3","tid":851471,"uid":73112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"呢啲成日誘惑人既賤女人一定要好好教訓下<br />\n起勢咁聞佢對大肉腳啲香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再含佢腳趾舔佢腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好就一一邊踩住我臉一邊囂張咁屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用碌鳩頂佢腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大屁股，淫奶又大又白 格肋底又滑又香 質個頭入去索 舔到佢啲淫肉全部都係口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用佢對淫奶同大臀肉打我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉+奶 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兩塊大臀肉同大淫奶玩臀交同夾腸同腋交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03533f2d22e39a396d09835076d8a4f322664c22","tid":851471,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"大波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cfd1041fd8658e89f59fab9ba599b846b58cd7","tid":851471,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c71bf1e9a1fdbbbcd16c4829d4d23d1fd3cfeb","tid":851471,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，呢隻麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c016a2dfc2d7808d049159a757dd96003d6a1e4f","tid":851471,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c5cd40c36f28e30eeaa4fb88eb9fafcc78223e","tid":851471,"uid":61235,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"大把台妹有得J<br />\n你係要搵件咁老黎J"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"老雞是沒有人要.jpg"},{"pid":"845ab3963112e41427c759e0f9ed127bc0de7a17","tid":851471,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"冇名冇ig?<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/212550_dd80031e2ff6fe21405b7605e405ab86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F212550_dd80031e2ff6fe21405b7605e405ab86.png&h=5edc5c0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e10230b62a81e3bd1160bce48d816902e0fbcc2","tid":851471,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"一般貨色姐.JPG"},{"pid":"32007cb12f4ca699b4915da6438f8e9237de326c","tid":851471,